Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D=`Откл.` then End
if shadow_cast=1 then shadow on else shadow off endif
if ac_accessory_debug then pen 10 addz ac_ref_height roty 90 rotz beta arrow=sqr((ac_ref_coords[1][3]-ac_ref_coords[1][1])^2+(ac_ref_coords[1][4]-ac_ref_coords[1][2])^2) cylind arrow-0.20, 0.02 addz arrow-0.20 cone 0.20, 0.05, 0, 90, 90 del 4 endif
pen gs_cont_pen
! ----------------------------- ! Do the covering with the cuts ! -----------------------------
diff_x=ac_whole_poly[1][7]-ac_whole_poly[1][1] diff_y=ac_whole_poly[1][8]-ac_whole_poly[1][2]
!print "diff_x=",diff_x !print "diff_y=",diff_y
if abs(diff_y)>eps and abs(diff_x)>eps then if ac_ref_coords[1][1]>ac_ref_coords[1][3] then extra=180 alfa=atn(diff_y/diff_x)+extra else if abs(diff_x)<eps then if diff_y>0 then alfa=90 else alfa=-90 endif endif if abs(diff_y)<eps then if diff_x>0 then alfa=0 else alfa=180 endif endif endif
! --------------- ! Do the covering ! ---------------
!u=whole_loc_poly[1][1] !v=whole_loc_poly[1][2] a_size=whole_loc_poly[1][7]-whole_loc_poly[1][1]-2*oversize b_size=whole_loc_poly[1][6]-whole_loc_poly[1][2]-2*oversize ins_diff=(whole_loc_poly[1][2]+oversize)*tan(ac_pitch)
addz wain_dist ! +height+thick for i=1 to vardim1(ac_coords) hotspot ac_coords[i][2],ac_coords[i][3],ac_coords[i][3]*tan(ac_pitch) next i del 1
group "geometry" put whole_loc_poly[1][1], whole_loc_poly[1][2], 15 put whole_loc_poly[1][3], whole_loc_poly[1][4], 15 put whole_loc_poly[1][5], whole_loc_poly[1][6], 15 put whole_loc_poly[1][7], whole_loc_poly[1][8], 15 put whole_loc_poly[1][1], whole_loc_poly[1][2], -1
for i=1 to crd_begend[1][2] if i<>crd_begend[1][2] then put loc_coords[i][2], loc_coords[i][3], 15 else put loc_coords[i][2], loc_coords[i][3], -1 endif next i
rotz delta addz ac_ref_height+ac_thickness+wain_dist+ins_diff-sgn(ac_pitch)*0.50 ! whole_loc_poly[1][1],whole_loc_poly[1][2], prism_ nsp/3, (whole_loc_poly[1][6]-whole_loc_poly[1][2]-2*oversize)*tan(ac_pitch)+sgn(ac_pitch)*1, get(nsp)
if vardim1(crd_begend)>1 then for j=2 to vardim1(crd_begend) for i=crd_begend[j][1] to crd_begend[j][2] if i<>crd_begend[1][2] then put loc_coords[i][2], loc_coords[i][3], 15 else put loc_coords[i][2], loc_coords[i][3], -1 endif next i
prism_ nsp/3, (whole_loc_poly[1][6]-whole_loc_poly[1][2]-2*oversize)*tan(ac_pitch)+sgn(ac_pitch)*1, get(nsp)
next j endif del 2 endgroup
if ac_accessory_debug then model wire placegroup "geometry" model solid endif
!!!!print " (a) a_size=",a_size," (b) b_size=",b_size," ac_pitch=",ac_pitch,"rooftype=",rooftype
material wain_mat group "covering" rotz delta if wain_pos=pvalue_1 then add whole_loc_poly[1][1]+oversize,whole_loc_poly[1][2]+oversize,ac_ref_height+ins_diff-wain_dist rotx ac_pitch call "Wainscot Finish" parameters a=a_size, b=b_size, ac_pitch=ac_pitch, wain_type_m=wain_type_m, wain_thk=wain_thk, wain_maxthk=wain_maxthk, wain_width=wain_width else !! Itt tartok add whole_loc_poly[1][1]+oversize,whole_loc_poly[1][2]+oversize,ac_ref_height+ins_diff-wain_dist rotx ac_pitch call "Wainscot Finish" parameters a=a_size, b=b_size, ac_pitch=ac_pitch, wain_type_m=wain_type_m, wain_thk=wain_thk, wain_maxthk=wain_maxthk, wain_width=wain_width endif del 3 endgroup
finish=subgroup("covering","geometry") placegroup finish
Symbol.Script_2D:
if ac_pitch<eps then !! Reference Basis Point unID=1 hotspot2 0,ref_direction[1][2],unID,ref_direction[1][1],1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -1,ref_direction[1][2],unID,ref_direction[1][1],3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1],ref_direction[1][2],unID,ref_direction[1][1],2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1],0,unID,ref_direction[1][2],1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1],-1,unID,ref_direction[1][2],3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1],ref_direction[1][2],unID,ref_direction[1][2],2 : unID=unID+1
!! Reference Vector hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1],ref_direction[1][2]+ref_direction[1][4],unID,ref_direction[1][3],1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1]-1,ref_direction[1][2]+ref_direction[1][4],unID,ref_direction[1][3],3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1]+ref_direction[1][3],ref_direction[1][2]+ref_direction[1][4],unID,ref_direction[1][3],2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1]+ref_direction[1][3],ref_direction[1][2],unID,ref_direction[1][4],1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1]+ref_direction[1][3],ref_direction[1][1]-1,unID,ref_direction[1][4],3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 ref_direction[1][1]+ref_direction[1][3],ref_direction[1][1]+ref_direction[1][4],unID,ref_direction[1][4],2 : unID=unID+1
line2 ref_direction[1][1],ref_direction[1][2],ref_direction[1][1]+ref_direction[1][3],ref_direction[1][2]+ref_direction[1][4] endif
! ------------- ! Making the 2D ! -------------
rot2 delta for i=1 to vardim1(loc_coords) hotspot2 loc_coords[i][2],loc_coords[i][3] next i
for i=1 to vardim1(loc_coords) if loc_coords[i][1]<1 1/2" then mask=1 else mask=-1 endif
put loc_coords[i][2], loc_coords[i][3], mask next i
pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type poly2_b{2} vardim1(loc_coords), 1+2+4+8+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, beta, get(nsp) del 1
end
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS=0.00001 main_cp_num=vardim1(ac_coords) cp_all_num=vardim1(ac_coords)
r=1 cp_num=0 for i=1 to vardim1(ac_coords) if ac_coords[i][1]>1 1/2" then cp_num=cp_num+1 next i
if cp_num=1 and (abs(ac_coords[1][2]-ac_coords[vardim1(ac_coords)][2])>eps Or abs(ac_coords[1][3]-ac_coords[vardim1(ac_coords)][3])>eps) then ac_coords[vardim1(ac_coords)][1]=1" last_line=vardim1(ac_coords)+1 ac_coords[last_line][1]=2" ac_coords[last_line][2]=ac_coords[1][2] ac_coords[last_line][3]=ac_coords[1][3] endif
!--------------! ! Inner Values ! !--------------!
values "wain_maxthk" range(wain_thk,wain_width/2) if wain_type<>`Панельная Обшивка 4` then hideparameter "wain_maxthk"
if gs_detlevel_3D=`Детальный` then gs_detlevel_3Dm=2 if gs_detlevel_3D=`Простой` then gs_detlevel_3Dm=1 if gs_detlevel_3D=`Откл.` then gs_detlevel_3Dm=0
if wain_type=`Панельная Обшивка 1` then wain_type_m=1 if wain_type=`Панельная Обшивка 2` then wain_type_m=2 if wain_type=`Панельная Обшивка 3` then wain_type_m=3 if wain_type=`Панельная Обшивка 4` then wain_type_m=4
pvalue_1=`Обшивка под Крышей` : pvalue_2=`Обшивка над Крышей` values "wain_pos" pvalue_1,pvalue_2
!------------------ ! Scan the polygons !------------------
exam=1 crd_end = 0 dim crd_begend[][] for i=1 to cp_num crd_num=0 crd_beg=crd_end+1 r=crd_beg
while ac_coords[r][1]>eps and ac_coords[r][1]<1 1/2" and exam<>0 do crd_num=crd_num+1 r=r+1 if r=vardim1(ac_coords) then exam=0 endif endwhile crd_end=crd_beg+crd_num
crd_begend[i][1]=crd_beg crd_begend[i][2]=crd_end next i
!------------------------------- ! Calculate the custom direction !-------------------------------
delta=0 if ac_pitch<eps then ref_length=sqr(ref_direction[1][3]^2+ref_direction[1][4]^2) if ref_direction[1][4]>=0 then delta=acs(ref_direction[1][3]/ref_length) else delta=360-acs(ref_direction[1][3]/ref_length) endif endif
! --------------------------------------------------- ! Scan the global boundary rectangle for the required ! boundary rectangle in the local coordinate system ! ---------------------------------------------------
oversize=0.5 ! Oversize for the cutting body
dim whole_loc_poly[][] dim loc_coords[][]
if ac_pitch<eps then if delta=0 then loc_coords=ac_coords else for num=1 to vardim1(ac_coords) loc_coords[num][1]=ac_coords[num][1] loc_coords[num][2]=ac_coords[num][2]*cos(delta)+ac_coords[num][3]*sin(delta) loc_coords[num][3]=-ac_coords[num][2]*sin(delta)+ac_coords[num][3]*cos(delta) next num endif else loc_coords=ac_coords endif
for i=1 to vardim1(loc_coords) put loc_coords[i][2] next i
min_x=min(use(nsp)) max_x=max(get(nsp))
for i=1 to vardim1(loc_coords) put loc_coords[i][3] next i
min_y=min(use(nsp)) max_y=max(get(nsp))
whole_loc_poly[1][1]=min_x-oversize whole_loc_poly[1][2]=min_y-oversize whole_loc_poly[1][3]=min_x-oversize whole_loc_poly[1][4]=max_y+oversize whole_loc_poly[1][5]=max_x+oversize whole_loc_poly[1][6]=max_y+oversize whole_loc_poly[1][7]=max_x+oversize whole_loc_poly[1][8]=min_y-oversize
if gs_gdl_debug then print "min_x=",min_x,"min_y=",min_y,"max_x=",max_x,"max_y=",max_y print whole_loc_poly[1][1],whole_loc_poly[1][2] print whole_loc_poly[1][3],whole_loc_poly[1][4] print whole_loc_poly[1][5],whole_loc_poly[1][6] print whole_loc_poly[1][7],whole_loc_poly[1][8] endif
!------------------------ ! Calculate the direction !------------------------
if (ac_ref_coords[1][3]-ac_ref_coords[1][1])>eps then if (ac_ref_coords[1][3]-ac_ref_coords[1][1])>0 then beta=atn((ac_ref_coords[1][4]-ac_ref_coords[1][2])/(ac_ref_coords[1][3]-ac_ref_coords[1][1])) endif if (ac_ref_coords[1][3]-ac_ref_coords[1][1])<0then beta=atn((ac_ref_coords[1][4]-ac_ref_coords[1][2])/(ac_ref_coords[1][3]-ac_ref_coords[1][1])) endif else beta=90 endif
!----------------------------------------------- ! Calculate the main size and number of elements !-----------------------------------------------
a_size=whole_loc_poly[1][7]-whole_loc_poly[1][1] b_size=whole_loc_poly[1][6]-whole_loc_poly[1][2]
if wain_type=`Панельная Обшивка 3` then y_size=0.14 else y_size=0.09 endif m=ceil(b_size/y_size) ! Number of ceiling
left_bot_x=ac_ref_coords[1][1]+whole_loc_poly[1][1]*cos(beta)-whole_loc_poly[1][2]*sin(beta) ! Calculate the left-bottom corner left_bot_y=ac_ref_coords[1][2]+whole_loc_poly[1][1]*sin(beta)+whole_loc_poly[1][2]*cos(beta) ! Calculate the left-bottom corner
